+
+Classify the canonical two-triad shared-mode seed families for the second
+budget under the frozen Step-1 equivalence rules and the Step-2 first-budget
+exclusions.
+
+## Success Criteria
+
+- State a canonical representative form for every genuinely new second-budget
+  seed family.
+- Separate true second-rung seeds from disguised first-budget dead seeds,
+  disconnected add-ons, and inert helical decorations.
+- Make the equivalence reductions explicit enough that the step result can cite
+  them directly.
+
+## Failure Criteria
