+  (d,-b) -> a,
+  (d,-a) -> b,
+  (a,c) -> e,
+  (e,-c) -> a,
+  (e,-a) -> c.
+  ```
+
+### Pass 1 - decisive cross-pair forcing
+
+- `[INFERRED]` The first genuinely new tests come from mixing the two seed
+  triads across the shared-mode ledger:
+
+  ```text
+  (d, c)  -> a + b + c,
+  (d,-c)  -> a + b - c,
